(3741, 113, 'service_details_card_0_card_title', 'Trademark Services:'),
(3742, 113, '_service_details_card_0_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3743, 113, 'service_details_card_0_card_content', 'We offer comprehensive trademark services to help you protect your brand identity. Our lawyers can assist with trademark searches and clearance to ensure the availability of your desired trademark. We handle the trademark registration process, including drafting and filing applications with the appropriate intellectual property offices. We also provide trademark monitoring and enforcement services to safeguard your trademarks against infringement.\r\n\r\n'),
(3744, 113, '_service_details_card_0_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3745, 113, 'service_details_card_1_card_title', 'Copyright Services:'),
(3746, 113, '_service_details_card_1_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3747, 113, 'service_details_card_1_card_content', 'Our lawyers provide guidance and support in copyright matters. We help you navigate copyright laws, register your original works with the relevant authorities, and enforce your copyright rights against unauthorized use or infringement. We assist with copyright licensing agreements, assignments, and addressing any copyright-related disputes that may arise.\r\n\r\n'),
(3748, 113, '_service_details_card_1_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3749, 113, 'service_details_card_2_card_title', 'Patent Services:'),
(3750, 113, '_service_details_card_2_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3751, 113, 'service_details_card_2_card_content', 'If you have an invention or innovative technology, our team can assist with patent protection. We provide strategic counsel on patentability, conduct patent searches, and draft and file patent applications. Our lawyers have experience in various industries and can effectively handle the complexities of the patent process. We also assist with patent portfolio management and enforcement to protect your inventions.\r\n\r\n'),
(3752, 113, '_service_details_card_2_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3753, 113, 'service_details_card_3_card_title', 'Trade Secret Protection:'),
(3754, 113, '_service_details_card_3_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3755, 113, 'service_details_card_3_card_content', 'We understand the value of trade secrets in maintaining a competitive edge. Our lawyers can help you identify and protect your trade secrets through comprehensive strategies, including confidentiality agreements, non-disclosure agreements (NDAs), and internal policies to safeguard sensitive information. We also provide guidance on trade secret enforcement and litigation if necessary.\r\n\r\n'),
(3756, 113, '_service_details_card_3_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3757, 113, 'service_details_card_4_card_title', 'IP Enforcement and Litigation:'),
(3758, 113, '_service_details_card_4_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3759, 113, 'service_details_card_4_card_content', 'If your intellectual property rights have been infringed upon, our lawyers are experienced in IP enforcement and litigation. We can represent you in pursuing legal remedies against infringers, including cease and desist letters, negotiation, mediation, arbitration, and litigation. Our goal is to protect your intellectual property rights and seek appropriate damages or injunctive relief.\r\n\r\n'),
(3760, 113, '_service_details_card_4_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
